HEADWORD: Countingroom
<hw>Count"ing*room`</hw> <pr>(kount"?ng-r??m`)</pr>, }</mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Count</er>, <pos>v.</pos>]</ety> <def>The
